name: task-decomposition
description: "Structured methodology for breaking complex requirements into
  actionable tasks with dependency mapping, effort estimation, and
  batch-creation-compatible JSON output. Use for: planning features, decomposing
  work, estimating effort, creating WBS-structured breakdowns. NOT for: task
  file operations (use rd3:tasks), business analysis, or system architecture."
version: 1.0.0
emoji: 🛠️
